		<title>CLARITY Act Poll: 52% Support, 70% Say US Should Have Passed Crypto Legislation</title>
		<link>https://news.bitcoin.com/clarity-act-poll-52-support-70-say-us-should-have-passed-crypto-legislation/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Kevin Helms]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 10 May 2026 18:34:40 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Regulation]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[CLARITY Act]]></category>
		<category><![CDATA[Congress]]></category>
